data.chText: 极受崇敬（或敬慕）的女人
data.enText: a woman who is loved or admired very much by other people
a screen goddess (= a female film/movie star)

simple_means.memory_skill: god 神 + ess 女性，雌性 → 女神

means: 极受崇敬(或敬慕)的女人

value.def: In many religions, a goddess is a female spirit or being that is believed to have power over a particular part of the world or nature.

trans: 杜尔迦女神；杜尔佳女神；德嘉女神
